## Troubleshooting

| Issue | Solution |
|---|---|
| `Missing required environment variables` | Ensure `fabric.yaml` has correct `datasetId` |
| `Query returned 0 rows` | Check table names match exactly; run DAX query directly in Semantic Model editor |
| `undefined is not an object (reading 'rows')` | One of your queries failed; check browser console for error details |
| `Rayfin error: unauthorized` | Verify you have read permissions on the semantic model in Fabric |
| `App runs but dashboard is blank` | Check `src/App.tsx` debug console output; look for `status: error` |

